pan&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;multiple&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;keys&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;to&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;multiple&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;values&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;only&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;none&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;of&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;the&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;keys&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;exist&lt;/span&gt;（将多个键设置为多个值，仅当这些键不存在时才设置）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;function&#34;&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;since&lt;/span&gt;: 1.0.1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;function&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;function&#34;&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;PSETEX&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;key&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;milliseconds&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;function&#34;&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;summary&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;Set&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;the&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;value&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;and&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;expiration&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;milliseconds&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;of&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;key&lt;/span&gt;（置键的值和到期时间(以毫秒为单位)）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&l